About Me
I'm a bilingual Graphic Designer with expertise in digital advertising, social media graphics, and landing page visuals. I combine traditional design tools with cutting-edge AI solutions to create visuals that are engaging, consistent, and perfectly aligned with brand identity.
My approach blends creativity with strategy, ensuring every design serves both aesthetic and business objectives.

Outside of work, I’m also the proud “mom” of a little dog named Lila — she keeps me on my toes and makes sure I never forget the importance of play and creativity.** 🐾💜

Designs Powered by AI
Prompt
"Create a photorealistic portrait of a young woman standing in a modern kitchen, holding a golden supplement capsule in one hand and a glass of water with lemon in the other. Add a glowing holographic brain highlighted on her head to symbolize cognitive health and supplement benefits. Natural light, ultra realistic style."
Prompt
"Generate a photorealistic image of a human brain placed on a wooden kitchen board, surrounded by healthy foods that support brain health: salmon fillet, blueberries, walnuts, egg, and lean beef. Natural kitchen background, daylight, hyper-realistic style, concept of nutrition for cognition."
